      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Hardware Layer\n\nRaspberry Pi GPIO: ST7920 Display, Buzzer, Buttons\nSTM32 (Serial): 8x Temperature Sensors (W1), 8x Dual LEDs (R/G), Power (VIN/VBAT)\nLIS2DH12 (I2C): Accelerometer (optional)",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Hardware Layer\n\nRaspberry Pi GPIO: ST7920 Display, Buzzer, Buttons\nSTM32 (Serial): 8x Temperature Sensors (W1), 8x Dual LEDs (R/G), Power (VIN/VBAT)\nLIS2DH12 (I2C): Accelerometer (optional)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 103
