      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Legend:\n\nBlue = Main app\nYellow = Config\nRed = Hardware drivers\nGreen = Monitor threads\nPurple = Optional\nOrange = Shared state\nGray = Hardware layer\n\nArrows:\n- Solid = Direct control\n- Dashed = Data flow",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Legend:\n\nBlue = Main app\nYellow = Config\nRed = Hardware drivers\nGreen = Monitor threads\nPurple = Optional\nOrange = Shared state\nGray = Hardware layer\n\nArrows:\n- Solid = Direct control\n- Dashed = Data flow",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
