      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Key Features:\n\n• Multi-threaded architecture\n• 8 temperature sensor monitoring\n• Alarm system with LED/buzzer\n• Power monitoring (AC/Battery)\n• LCD display with QR codes\n• SQLite data persistence\n• YAML configuration\n• Priority-based buzzer alerts",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Key Features:\n\n• Multi-threaded architecture\n• 8 temperature sensor monitoring\n• Alarm system with LED/buzzer\n• Power monitoring (AC/Battery)\n• LCD display with QR codes\n• SQLite data persistence\n• YAML configuration\n• Priority-based buzzer alerts",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 143
    }
